His cousin has a grade eight flute exam next week. She wants him to.accompany her free of charge. Ken isn't sure if he should do it but he doesn't want to pull the rug out from under her. My friend Eddie has been having a crush on this girl named Jo for seven years. He's still holding out false hope that one day he will become her boyfriend but she has a boyfriend. He's just being a doormat. During their trip to Thailand eddie bought lots of presents and keepsakes for her and paid for all her meals but at the end he ran out of money and so had to ask Jo to lend him some money who's now saying that he's staying close to her to take advantage of her and her money. They stayed in a twin room which has a pair of twin beds rather than a double bed. She told him that she wouldn't sleep with any guy until she was married which we know isn't true; she sleeps with her real boyfriend daily. Eddie knew it wasn't true but didn't mind. Ger expression looked immediately different because she got what she wanted already. She pretended to be cute and said "we can do facials together sweetheart..." then he got persuaded. He studied higher diploma in Australia but besides IT he failed all the exams and failed them again in his resits so he couldn't apply for a student visa again. He ended up working as a security guard in a residential building whose salary is twelve thousand dollars a month. Recently he said he wanted to take a shot at the CPA exam and become an accountant with better career prospects. It'll improve his job prospects but the next day he said it'd be a waste of time if he failed it so he gave up. The problem is he doesn't want to step out of his comfort zone; he'd rather be an ordinary security guard for the rest of his life. In addition he's extremely thin; he's 180 centimetres tall but weighs less than 110 pounds. I suggested he gain weight but he didn't listen. I tried to encourage him but to no effect.
